Jainism and buddhism
--------------------
Jainism
    Mahavira
        539-467 
        24th thirthankara
        kundagrama near vaishali
        parents siddhartha and trisala
        married yasodha and birth to daughter
        13 year of penance - Kevala gnana
        Died at Pava near rajgriha
        
        Triratnas
            faith
            knowledge 
            conduct
                5 great vows
                    not to ijure life
                    not to lie
                    not to steal
                    not to acquire property
                    not to lead immoral life
                    
        First jain council - Pataliputra by Sthulabahu
        Second jain council - Valabhi
            Final completion of 12 angas 
            
 Buddha
    567-487
    lumbini garden near kapilavasthu
    father sudhodhana of sakya clan and mom mayadevi
    aunt prajaati gautami
    Married yashodhara and son rahula
    age 29 
    nirvana at 35
    first sermon at sarnath near benares t
    died at Kusinagara
    
    4 noble truths
        world is full of suffering
        cause of suffering is desire
        if desire is rid off suffering an be removed
        follow eightfold path
            view
            resolve
            speech
            conduct
            livelihood
            effort
            mindfulness
            concentration
            
     first buddhist council - rajgriha - Mahakasapa
